# MongoDB Database Design — Helperland (Working-Desk)

## Overview

13 collections replacing the flat `db.json` file. Supports multi-role users (Customer, Service Provider, Admin), dynamic service categories (Fan, Cupboard, Bed, Ceiling, Cleaning, etc.), bookings, payments, reviews, and notifications.

---

## 1. `users`

```js
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  firstName: String,              // required
  lastName: String,               // required
  email: String,                  // required, unique, indexed
  mobile: String,                 // required
  password: String,               // bcrypt hashed, required
  role: String,                   // enum: "customer" | "service_provider" | "admin"
  status: String,                 // enum: "active" | "inactive" | "blocked"
  avatar: String,                 // image URL or avatar code
  gender: String,                 // enum: "male" | "female" | "other"
  dateOfBirth: Date,
  preferredLanguage: String,      // enum: "English" | "Hindi" | "Gujarati"

  // Service Provider specific
  bio: String,
  experience: Number,             // years
  serviceCategories: [ObjectId],  // → service_categories
  serviceAreas: [String],         // postal codes they serve
  averageRating: Number,          // denormalized, default 0
  totalCompletedJobs: Number,     // denormalized, default 0
  blockList: [ObjectId],          // → users (blocked customer IDs)

  // SP address (embedded)
  address: {
    streetName: String,
    houseNumber: String,
    city: String,
    postalCode: String,
    state: String
  },

  // Security
  resetPasswordToken: String,
  resetPasswordExpires: Date,
  lastLoginAt: Date,

  createdAt: Date,                // auto
  updatedAt: Date                 // auto
}
// Indexes: { email: 1 } unique, { role: 1, status: 1 }, { serviceAreas: 1 }
```

---

## 2. `service_categories`

Top-level and sub-categories for all services offered.

```js
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  name: String,                   // "Fan Service", "Home Cleaning"
  slug: String,                   // "fan-service" — unique, URL-friendly
  description: String,
  icon: String,                   // icon name or URL
  image: String,                  // banner image URL
  parentCategory: ObjectId,       // null = top-level, ObjectId = sub-category

  basePrice: Number,              // price per hour in ₹
  discountPercent: Number,        // default discount
  estimatedDuration: Number,      // default hours

  isActive: Boolean,              // default true
  sortOrder: Number,              // display ordering

  createdAt: Date,
  updatedAt: Date
}
// Indexes: { slug: 1 } unique, { parentCategory: 1 }, { isActive: 1 }
```

