## 3. `services`

Individual service items / add-ons within a category.

```js
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  categoryId: ObjectId,           // → service_categories
  name: String,                   // "Inside Cabinet Cleaning"
  description: String,
  price: Number,                  // price for this item
  priceType: String,              // enum: "per_hour" | "fixed" | "per_unit"
  duration: Number,               // estimated minutes
  isAddon: Boolean,               // true = optional extra service
  isActive: Boolean,
  image: String,

  createdAt: Date,
  updatedAt: Date
}
// Indexes: { categoryId: 1 }, { isAddon: 1, isActive: 1 }
```

Replaces the hardcoded `ExtraService` object. Current extras become `isAddon: true` under Home Cleaning:
- Inside Cabinets, Inside Fridge, Inside Oven, Laundry Wash & Dry, Interior Windows

