## 4. `addresses`

Customer/SP saved addresses.

```js
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  userId: ObjectId,               // → users
  label: String,                  // "Home" | "Office" | "Other"
  houseNumber: String,
  streetName: String,
  city: String,
  state: String,
  postalCode: String,
  mobileNumber: String,
  latitude: Number,               // for future map integration
  longitude: Number,
  isDefault: Boolean,             // default false

  createdAt: Date,
  updatedAt: Date
}
// Indexes: { userId: 1 }, { postalCode: 1 }
```

---

## 5. `bookings`

Main booking/order collection — replaces `Bookservice`.

```js
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  bookingNumber: Number,          // auto-generated human-readable ID

  // Participants
  customerId: ObjectId,           // → users
  serviceProviderId: ObjectId,    // → users (null until SP accepts)

  // Service details
  categoryId: ObjectId,           // → service_categories
  selectedServices: [{
    serviceItemId: ObjectId,      // → services
    name: String,                 // denormalized
    quantity: Number,
    price: Number
  }],

  // Schedule
  scheduledDate: Date,
  scheduledTime: String,          // "10:30 AM"
  serviceHours: Number,
  totalTime: Number,              // including extras

  // Location
  serviceAddress: {
    addressId: ObjectId,          // → addresses
    fullAddress: String,          // denormalized display string
    postalCode: String,
    contactMobile: String
  },

  // Pricing
  subtotal: Number,
  discountPercent: Number,
  discountAmount: Number,
  couponId: ObjectId,             // → coupons
  couponCode: String,
  totalAmount: Number,            // final payable

  // Metadata
  comments: String,
  hasPets: Boolean,
  photos: [String],               // uploaded photo URLs

  // Status lifecycle
  status: String,                 // enum: "new" | "accepted" | "in_progress" |
                                  //       "completed" | "cancelled" | "rescheduled"
  statusHistory: [{
    status: String,
    changedBy: ObjectId,
    reason: String,
    timestamp: Date
  }],

  // Cancellation
  cancellationReason: String,
  cancelledBy: ObjectId,

  // Reschedule
  rescheduleNotes: String,
  rescheduledFrom: { date: Date, time: String },

  // Rating
  rating: Number,                 // 1–5
  review: String,
  ratedAt: Date,

  createdAt: Date,
  updatedAt: Date
}
// Indexes: { customerId: 1, status: 1 }, { serviceProviderId: 1, status: 1 },
//          { "serviceAddress.postalCode": 1, status: 1 }, { scheduledDate: 1 },
//          { bookingNumber: 1 } unique
```

---

## 6. `payments`

Payment transaction records (Razorpay integration).

```js
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  bookingId: ObjectId,            // → bookings
  customerId: ObjectId,           // → users

  orderId: String,                // Razorpay order ID
  paymentId: String,              // Razorpay payment ID
  signature: String,              // Razorpay signature

  amount: Number,
  currency: String,               // default "INR"
  method: String,                 // "card" | "upi" | "netbanking" | "wallet" | "cod"
  status: String,                 // "pending" | "completed" | "failed" | "refunded"

  refundId: String,
  refundAmount: Number,
  refundReason: String,

  metadata: Object,               // raw gateway response

  createdAt: Date,
  updatedAt: Date
}
// Indexes: { bookingId: 1 }, { paymentId: 1 } unique, { customerId: 1 }
```

---

## 7. `coupons`

Discount coupon management (admin-created).

```js
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  code: String,                   // "WELCOME20" — unique, uppercase
  discountPercent: Number,        // 1–100
  maxDiscountAmount: Number,      // cap on discount
  minOrderAmount: Number,         // minimum to apply
  maxUsage: Number,               // total allowed uses
  usedCount: Number,              // current uses
  perUserLimit: Number,           // max per customer

  applicableCategories: [ObjectId], // → service_categories (empty = all)

  isActive: Boolean,
  startsAt: Date,
  expiresAt: Date,

  createdBy: ObjectId,            // → users (admin)
  createdAt: Date,
  updatedAt: Date
}
// Indexes: { code: 1 } unique, { isActive: 1, expiresAt: 1 }
```

---

## 8. `coupon_usages`

Tracks per-user coupon redemptions.

```js
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  couponId: ObjectId,             // → coupons
  userId: ObjectId,               // → users
  bookingId: ObjectId,            // → bookings
  discountAmount: Number,
  usedAt: Date
}
// Indexes: { couponId: 1, userId: 1 }
```

---

## 9. `reviews`

Separated review/rating collection for aggregation.

```js
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  bookingId: ObjectId,            // → bookings
  customerId: ObjectId,           // → users (reviewer)
  serviceProviderId: ObjectId,    // → users (reviewed)
  categoryId: ObjectId,           // → service_categories

  rating: Number,                 // 1–5
  comment: String,

  spReply: String,                // SP response
  spRepliedAt: Date,

  isVisible: Boolean,             // admin can hide

  createdAt: Date,
  updatedAt: Date
}
// Indexes: { serviceProviderId: 1, rating: 1 }, { customerId: 1 }, { categoryId: 1 }
```

---

## 10. `service_areas`

Serviceable postal codes — replaces `postalCode` array.

```js
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  postalCode: String,             // "395010" — unique
  city: String,                   // "Surat"
  state: String,                  // "Gujarat"
  isActive: Boolean,

  availableCategories: [ObjectId], // → service_categories available here

  createdAt: Date,
  updatedAt: Date
}
// Indexes: { postalCode: 1 } unique, { city: 1 }
```

---

## 11. `notifications`

Email/SMS/push notification log.

```js
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  userId: ObjectId,               // recipient → users
  type: String,                   // "booking_confirmed" | "booking_accepted" |
                                  // "booking_cancelled" | "payment_received" |
                                  // "rating_received" | "password_reset"
  title: String,
  message: String,

  channel: String,                // "email" | "sms" | "push" | "in_app"
  status: String,                 // "sent" | "delivered" | "failed" | "read"

  relatedBookingId: ObjectId,
  metadata: Object,               // email subject, SMS sid, etc.

  readAt: Date,
  createdAt: Date
}
// Indexes: { userId: 1, readAt: 1 }, { createdAt: -1 }
```

---

## 12. `faqs`

Frequently asked questions (admin-managed).

```js
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  question: String,
  answer: String,
  categoryId: ObjectId,           // optional → service_categories
  sortOrder: Number,
  isActive: Boolean,

  createdAt: Date,
  updatedAt: Date
}
// Indexes: { isActive: 1, sortOrder: 1 }
```

---

## 13. `blocked_customers`

SP-to-customer block relationships — replaces `Block-user`.

```js
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  serviceProviderId: ObjectId,    // → users (SP who blocked)
  customerId: ObjectId,           // → users (blocked customer)
  reason: String,

  createdAt: Date,
  updatedAt: Date
}
// Indexes: { serviceProviderId: 1, customerId: 1 } unique compound
```

---

## Entity Relationships

```
users 1──N addresses
users 1──N bookings (as customer)
users 1──N bookings (as service_provider)
users N──M service_categories (SP skills)
users 1──N blocked_customers (as SP)
users 1──N notifications

service_categories 1──N services
service_categories 1──N service_categories (parent → child)
service_categories N──M service_areas

bookings 1──1 payments
bookings 1──1 reviews
bookings N──1 service_categories
bookings N──1 coupons → coupon_usages

faqs N──1 service_categories (optional)
```

---

## Migration: db.json → MongoDB

| Old (`db.json`) | New (MongoDB) |
|---|---|
| `user[]` | `users` |
| `postalCode[]` | `service_areas` |
| `Bookservice[]` | `bookings` + `payments` |
| `Address[]` | `addresses` |
| `Block-user[]` | `blocked_customers` |
| `coupon[]` | `coupons` + `coupon_usages` |
| `faq[]` | `faqs` |
| Hardcoded extras | `service_categories` + `services` |
| *(none)* | `reviews`, `notifications`, `payments` |

---

## Collection Summary

| # | Collection | Replaces | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | `users` | `user` array | All user accounts with role-based fields |
| 2 | `service_categories` | *(new)* | Fan, Cupboard, Bed, Ceiling, Cleaning, etc. |
| 3 | `services` | Hardcoded `ExtraService` | Individual service items/add-ons per category |
| 4 | `addresses` | `Address` array | User saved addresses |
| 5 | `bookings` | `Bookservice` array | Service booking orders |
| 6 | `payments` | *(new)* | Payment transactions (Razorpay) |
| 7 | `coupons` | `coupon` (inline) | Discount codes |
| 8 | `coupon_usages` | *(new)* | Track per-user coupon usage |
| 9 | `reviews` | Rating field on booking | Dedicated rating and review system |
| 10 | `service_areas` | `postalCode` array | Serviceable postal codes with city/state |
| 11 | `notifications` | *(new)* | Email/SMS/push notification log |
| 12 | `faqs` | `faq` (inline) | Frequently asked questions |
| 13 | `blocked_customers` | `Block-user` / `BlockList` | SP-to-customer block relationships |
